{"lastModified":1760024828067,"uri":"c::18277099312::vessel::95ceedb0-a8b8-11ef-a232-8933728c6716","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nLagoon 43 Wanderer, a brand-new model from Lagoon Catamarans that epitomizes versatility and adaptability. With its modular design, this innovative vessel allows you to customize the space according to your preferences, seamlessly linking the interior and exterior areas. This creates a welcoming living environment ideal for gatherings with friends and family, complete with a dining table that accommodates up to 12 guests.\n\nLagoon 43 Wanderer features a newly designed hull that maximizes interior volume, providing spacious berths and flexible living areas. In the owner’s cabin, a generous forward berth is complemented by an en-suite head and shower located at the aft, ensuring a peaceful sanctuary away from engine noise. The fully equipped galley includes a stove, oven, fridge, freezer, sink, ice maker, and coffee maker, making culinary endeavors effortless. With air conditioning and heating available throughout the boat, comfort is guaranteed in any climate.\n\nThis catamaran showcases its signature design with innovative solutions for easy access and fluid movement between the boat and the dock. Notably, Lagoon 43 incorporates an additional aft entryway for each hull, seamlessly integrated into the boat's elegant lines, enhancing both functionality and visual appeal. Whether you're sailing or hosting, the Lagoon 43 offers a stylish and comfortable space for unforgettable moments on the water.","blueprint":{"name":"WANDERER","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::95ceedb0-a8b8-11ef-a232-8933728c6716::assets::54cd69b0-a8c0-11ef-9fde-85775c757b17/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::95ceedb0-a8b8-11ef-a232-8933728c6716::assets::54cf6580-a8c0-11ef-8740-878d3f523001/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::95ceedb0-a8b8-11ef-a232-8933728c6716::assets::54cf8c90-a8c0-11ef-